stages

$project = specific field
$match = filter(reduce) number of docs. remove duplicate
$limit = limit number of docs
$unwind = splits array into one doc for each element in the array
$group = group docs by distinct key(primary key)
$sort = returns input docs to sorted order(ascending/descending)
$out = last stage, creates/replaces unsharded collection with input docs

arithmetic
abs, add, sub, mul, div

group
sum, avg, max, min, first, last

date
year, month, week, hour, minute, second

comparison
eq, lt, lte, gt, gte

boolean
and, or